{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 ReaticulateAdapter\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Script that connects "Reaticulate" to "Pie Menu 3000", allowing for dynamic generation of an articulations pie menu depending on active bank.\line Also generates a channel/available banks menu, it'll default to this one if there is no active bank. Can also be bind to have quick access to other MIDI Channels and their respective banks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Prerequisites\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Reaticulate} and {\b Pie Menu 3000}\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Mesh of v6 with a few v7 bits. Focused on v6 behavior.\par}
}

